title: Line-waiting Apple fanatics rush to grab new iPhones in annual rite of commercial self-flagellation
text: New iPhones. Same lines. After eight years of watching people lining up for new iPhones, what is there left to say? Let’s just go to the social media things and enjoy the nonsense.
